Method Overriding
1. Done in two seperate classes
2. Runtime polymorphism
3. Rules 
    The complete method signature should be the same in both classes
    Number, types, order of parameters should be the same.
4. Can use the annotation "@override" to check.


Method Overload
1. done in the same class
2. Compile time polymorphism
3. Rules
    The Number, type, order of parameters have to be different.